      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Harput'un en bilinen simgelerinden biri olan Harput Kalesi'nin yap\u0131m\u0131
    s\u0131ras\u0131nda, kurakl\u0131k nedeniyle harc\u0131nda su yerine ba\u015Fka
    bir s\u0131v\u0131 kullan\u0131ld\u0131\u011F\u0131 efsanesi g\xFCn\xFCm\xFCze
    kadar ula\u015Fm\u0131\u015Ft\u0131r. Bu efsaneye dayanarak Harput Kalesi halk
    aras\u0131nda hangi isimle de an\u0131lmaktad\u0131r?"
